# .varlock
#
# Varlock secret definitions for harihoudini.dev.
#
# Usage:
#   Local dev:    pnpm varlock:pull  (writes to .env.local)
#   Update vault: pnpm varlock:push
#
# Each line: KEY  required|optional  type  Description
#
# Required at runtime (absent during `next build` in CI — that is intentional).
DATABASE_URL       required  string  Supabase PostgreSQL connection string. Append ?pgBouncer=true for Lambda.
PAYLOAD_SECRET     required  string  Payload JWT signing secret. Minimum 32 characters.
NEXT_PUBLIC_SERVER_URL  required  string  Public canonical URL. https://harihoudini.dev in production.

# Required in production only — provisioned by SST, injected by Varlock at deploy time.
S3_BUCKET          optional  string  SST-provisioned S3 bucket name for Payload media uploads.
S3_REGION          optional  string  AWS region. Defaults to us-east-1.

# Local development only — not needed in Lambda (IAM role provides credentials).
AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID      optional  string  AWS IAM access key for local S3 testing.
AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY  optional  string  AWS IAM secret for local S3 testing.
